n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"pod_processes\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio和client_error_ratio出现极端异常，P99变化率达到200%，表明该Pod存在严重错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-0的error_ratio从正常P99 0.0激增至故障期P99 50.53，变化率200%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend服务集群\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max和rrt指标在所有frontend实例上均出现显著异常，P99变化率均超过190%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0/1/2的rrt_max P99从约29-30万激增至4800万以上，rrt P99从1.3-1.4万激增至59-66万\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"pod_processes指标显示进程状态变化，虽然数值未变但P99分布发生变化，可能指示Pod重启或异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"redis-cart-0的pod_processes P99从2.0变为1.0，变化率66.67%\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现：**\n\n1. **最严重的异常**：`shippingservice-0` 的错误率指标异常显著，error_ratio和client_error_ratio的P99变化率高达200%，表明该Pod存在严重故障。\n\n2. **性能瓶颈**：所有frontend实例的响应时间指标(rrt_max和rrt)都出现极端恶化，P99响应时间从几十万激增至数千万，变化率均超过190%，说明前端服务受到严重影响。\n\n3. **Pod生命周期异常**：`redis-cart-0`的pod_processes指标显示进程状态变化，可能指示Pod重启或异常状态。\n\n根据故障模式识别规则，`shippingservice-0`的错误率异常是最直接的故障信号，而frontend服务的性能恶化可能是其下游依赖故障的连锁反应。\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\n基于收集到的追踪数据，我已经成功获取了故障时间段内的异常调用链信息。现在让我分析这些数据来识别根因：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->recommendationservice\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"recommendationservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"recommendationservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"推荐服务响应时间从正常的142ms激增到11.1秒，延迟倍数达到78倍，是系统中最严重的延迟瓶颈\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"产品目录服务在ListProducts操作中响应时间从2秒激增到19.8秒，延迟倍数达到10,000倍，表明严重性能问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端服务出现大量HTTP 500错误和context canceled错误，表明下游服务超时导致前端请求失败\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现分析：\n\n### 1. **最严重的延迟瓶颈**\n- **recommendationservice**: 响应时间从142ms激增到11.1秒（78倍延迟）\n- **productcatalogservice**: ListProducts操作从2ms激增到19.8秒（10,000倍延迟）\n\n### 2. **错误传播路径**\n- 前端服务（frontend）接收到大量HTTP 500错误\n- 错误状态码显示\"context canceled\"，表明下游服务超时导致请求被取消\n\n### 3. **调用链依赖关系**\n```\nFrontend → RecommendationService → ProductCatalogService\n```\n- 推荐服务依赖于产品目录服务，两者都出现严重延迟\n- 前端服务作为入口点，受到下游服务延迟的连锁影响\n\n### 4. **根因定位**\n基于拓扑分析，ProductCatalogService作为最下游的服务出现最严重的延迟（10,000倍），很可能是问题的初始根源，导致RecommendationService超时，最终影响Frontend服务。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "099ce7e2-274", "component": "shippingservice-0", "reason": "error_ratio and client_error_ratio spike (P99 0.0 to 50.53, 200% change rate) indicating pod lifecycle issues", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LoadMetrics(shippingservice-0)", "observation": "error_ratio P99 increased from 0.0 to 50.53, client_error_ratio 200% change rate indicating severe anomalies"}, {"step": 2, "action": "LogSearch(frontend)", "observation": "All frontend services show rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled indicating downstream service unavailability"}, {"step": 3, "action": "TraceAnalysis(099ce7e2-274)", "observation": "Frontend services show HTTP 500 errors and context canceled errors due to downstream service failures"}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
